1
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,280
You know,

2
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,359
all the way here,

3
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,760
we haven't seen any rain.

4
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,840
Just mountains and dirt slopes,

5
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,640
all pretty dry.

6
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,959
Why is this place so damp?

7
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:23,359
We always end up in godforsaken places.

8
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:25,519
With all this weird, spooky stuff,

9
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,200
how can you not imagine things?

10
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:30,480
Go ask her to check the map.

11
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,120
He Shutong,

12
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:38,439
Chiyan Jizhou is so vast.

13
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,480
Where do we go from here?

14
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:48,640
This is the map from the Rahu Hall.

15
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,359
I copied it from the mask.

16
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:53,319
I didn't know what place it showed before,

17
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:54,560
so I just kept it on me.

18
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,920
Now it seems

19
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,519
it must be Chiyan Jizhou.

20
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:02,400
Chiyan Jizhou is circular.

21
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:06,079
So what's at the center?

22
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,879
The Mengna Valley people loved ceremonies.

23
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,120
This center

24
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,560
must be where they

25
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,280
held grand rituals, the Altar Site.

26
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:15,080
The Altar Site.

27
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:36,840
Why is it getting more humid here?

28
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:41,759
Don't tell me more poison bugs are coming.

29
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,840
Relax, Old Lu.

30
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,800
It's just water vapor.

31
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,800
Everyone, stay close. Don't get separated.

32
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,000
What the heck?

33
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,199
Where's this smoke coming from?

34
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:02,199
Where is everyone?

35
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:02,960
Old Lu!

36
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,319
Old Lu!

37
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,080
What's going on?

38
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,479
Smells like a smoke bomb.

39
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,800
Someone's definitely up to something.

40
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,479
It must be Bi Huaqiang.

41
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:18,000
He grabbed the smoke bombs in the chaos.

42
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,840
Uncle Min must know what's at the Altar Site,

43
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,159
so he wants to get there before us.

44
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,240
Everyone just learned from you

45
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,439
that this terrain is circular,

46
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,520
and the Altar Site is at the center.

47
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,719
He knows the route and wants to ditch us.

48
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:28,000
No time to waste. Let's move.

49
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,039
Fatty and Old Lu aren't here yet.

50
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,879
With their experience, if they lose us,

51
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:33,159
they'll definitely head to the center.

52
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:33,800
Besides,

53
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,319
Uncle Min is already heading there.

54
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,719
He just wants to take the Lingxiao Pearl.

55
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,599
If it really is at the Altar Site

56
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,479
and he takes it,

57
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,840
it'd be a massive blow to our search

58
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,280
for the Mengna Valley civilization.

59
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,560
We have to get there first.

60
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,039
Are you worried about losing artifacts,

61
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:47,199
or worried about me?

62
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,360
The Altar Site is just ahead.

63
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,040
The idol of the Mengna Valley people

64
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,879
is a winged serpent.

65
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,040
And these stone pillars,

66
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,160
what do they mean?

67
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,600
Shutong,

68
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:03,120
how do these statues tie to Mengna Valley?

69
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:05,160
What Mengna Valley worshipped

70
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,680
was a serpent with bat wings.

71
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:11,000
All prehistoric civilization legends

72
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,360
unanimously believe

73
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,480
that gods created everything.

74
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,319
But why would Mengna Valley

75
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:20,199
worship a serpent?

76
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,560
Slow, slow down.

77
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:24,720
Slow down!

78
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:38,120
A fake snake? Seriously?

79
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:45,079
Is this the meeting spot?

80
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,879
This place is huge.

81
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:48,160
Only this spot looks like the Altar Site.

82
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,240
Where else could it be?

83
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:54,800
What the... what?

84
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,480
Who tapped me?

85
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,279
What's the deal?

86
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,480
Hey, don't mess with me!

87
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,240
He Shutong.

88
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,399
You're picking up bad habits from Chen!

89
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:06,079
My heart can't take this!

90
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,959
I'm gonna collapse right here.

91
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,040
Sorry about that.

92
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,720
Where's that old fox Uncle Min?

93
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,519
Did he throw the smoke bomb?

94
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:14,959
Must've been him.

95
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,319
No idea where he's hiding now.

96
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,000
What took you two so long?

97
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,079
Don't even ask.

98
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:21,519
This place is seriously creepy.

99
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:22,879
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

100
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:24,480
Guess what we found.

101
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,319
Old Lu, come up and look.

102
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:31,319
Why's there a pot of stewed beef here?

103
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,680
It's empty.

104
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,720
An optical illusion.

105
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,560
Just like that cave in Yunling,

106
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,160
where you saw that fake face.

107
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:46,879
No, no, no.

108
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:48,720
This is different from Yunling.

109
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,240
The one in the Yunling cave,

110
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,319
you could tell the builders

111
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:53,439
made it on purpose to scare people.

112
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,920
But this one...

113
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:57,720
Who'd scare people with fake beef stew?

114
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:00,639
What else did you find that's fake?

115
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:02,879
Everything else,

116
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,800
the stones are real,

117
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,120
the walls are real,

118
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:07,399
the thick fog is real,

119
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:10,480
the Altar Site is real too.

120
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:13,439
Old Lu, got any cans left?

121
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,120
Yeah, I do.

122
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,360
Have some, go ahead.

123
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:15,879
Toss me one.

124
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,920
I've got crackers too.

125
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,920
Is this one beef?

126
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:24,240
It's empty.

127
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:39,759
This one's empty too.

128
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,680
This whole city is fake!

129
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,839
So this entire huge area

130
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,480
is just one big shrine.

131
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:48,600
It's not Chiyan Jizhou at all.

132
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:12,199
This statue is tilted.

133
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:22,720
Someone's been here.

134
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,879
There must've been something here

135
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:26,920
that someone took.

136
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,439
What was taken?

137
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:29,800
My guess is,

138
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:33,200
it relates to Mengna Valley's history,

139
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,279
the Altar Site, or even the Lingxiao Pearl.

140
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:41,080
Seems we all underestimated Uncle Min.

141
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,720
This book isn't made of paper.

142
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:45,120
Looks like some kind of animal hide.

143
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,919
Can you read it?

144
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:49,360
These symbols

145
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,120
must be Mengna Valley hieroglyphs.

146
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,120
Does it mention the Lingxiao Pearl?

147
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,000
Godfather, this book is too thick.

148
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,440
It's full of these symbols.

149
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:59,480
We'll need He Shutong's help.

150
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,720
Godfather, honestly, just now,

151
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,240
you shouldn't have used that smoke bomb.

152
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,480
Without He Shutong,

153
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:05,639
we still can't crack

154
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:06,720
its secrets. What do you know?

155
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,799
They've got all the weapons and manpower.

156
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,960
The closer we get to the truth,

157
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,720
the more likely they'll ditch us.

158
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:15,000
This book is our only bargaining chip.

159
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,799
Let's move!

160
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:17,240
Hurry, this way!

161
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,559
Don't move.

162
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,360
Where are they?

163
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,000
Hey, brothers.

164
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,440
You know why I'm here?

165
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,919
We're short-handed inside.

166
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:26,159
I came to get you.

167
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,399
Brother Chen's inside.

168
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,919
He's found tons of stuff.

169
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,159
Come on, follow me.

170
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,360
We're really short-handed in there.

171
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,000
You need to find a vehicle here.

172
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,519
Let me explain.

173
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,600
An Xiang, keep up!

174
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,039
We don't have enough vehicles.

175
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,360
He's discovered so many things.

176
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,399
You get what I mean?

177
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,039
Nobody move!

178
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,879
What's going on here?

179
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:18,360
Attacking people in broad daylight?

180
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,240
You think out in the wilderness,

181
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,720
you can do whatever you want?

182
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:27,000
Brother Chen, you sure move fast.

183
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,799
Let me tell you all,

184
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,759
I've got something in my hands right now.

185
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,559
An Xiang.

186
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,919
It's that book she's holding.

187
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:39,399
To unlock the secret of Mengna Valley,

188
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,600
not only do I need it,

189
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:42,080
but you need it even more.

190
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,840
This isn't the real Chiyan Jizhou at all.

191
00:10:45,799 --> 00:10:47,360
That place you just visited

192
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:48,840
isn't where the Mengna Valley people

193
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,320
held their grand ceremonies either.

194
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,519
This Chiyan Jizhou simply doesn't exist.

195
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,200
It's all an illusion.

196
00:10:54,519 --> 00:10:56,320
Then where's the real Chiyan Jizhou?

197
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,840
That depends on what this book says.

198
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:07,840
Brother Chen,

199
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:10,519
take a look at the situation now.

200
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,799
The weapons are in my hands,

201
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:16,360
and the key to the Chiyan Jizhou mystery

202
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,720
is also in my hands.

203
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,879
So wouldn't you say

204
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,159
I'm in a position to negotiate now?

205
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,919
To keep things fair,

206
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,399
you can read this book,

207
00:11:28,679 --> 00:11:30,399
but I have to be the one who keeps it.

208
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:36,600
What do you say, is that acceptable?

209
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:39,919
Deal.

210
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,399
Great, thank you.

211
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,639
Miss He.

212
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,200
Can you actually read this or not?

213
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:04,159
These should be pictographs.

214
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,879
The style resembles ancient rock art.

215
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:11,720
Is this book made of animal hide?

216
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,039
Quite possibly.

217
00:12:14,039 --> 00:12:16,440
The Kunlun Mountains don't suit farming.

218
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,279
So logically speaking,

219
00:12:18,399 --> 00:12:20,000
they must have lived by hunting.

220
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:22,639
So hide-made books were easy to carry.

221
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,559
That's possible too.

222
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,399
Judging from these characters,

223
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,759
they haven't faded in thousands of years.

224
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,440
Technically speaking,

225
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,960
they used materials like Dunhuang murals.

226
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,840
Master Lu,

227
00:12:35,759 --> 00:12:39,440
I think the book's origin and materials

228
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,759
don't really matter anymore.

229
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:41,639
What matters is finding out

230
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:43,639
what it actually says.

231
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,720
This book tells the origin of Mengna Valley.

232
00:12:48,159 --> 00:12:51,039
Long ago, people in the Kunlun Mountains

233
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,159
were attacked by a giant serpent.

234
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:56,039
One person used a mysterious pearl

235
00:12:56,039 --> 00:12:57,120
to subdue the serpent.

236
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,759
He gained the serpent's power,

237
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:01,000
and inside the pit where the serpent grew,

238
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:02,279
he founded Mengna Valley,

239
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,519
becoming the king of Mengna Valley.

240
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,519
Under the king, the Mengna Valley people

241
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:08,639
held a grand ceremony every year,

242
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:10,279
similar to the Fengshan rites,

243
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:13,240
to pray to the serpent god for blessings.

244
00:13:14,159 --> 00:13:18,000
This snake drawing is so exaggerated.

245
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,519
It's bigger than a dinosaur.

246
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:21,200
Ancient records of history

247
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:23,480
always contain exaggeration and flair.

248
00:13:23,639 --> 00:13:25,000
Plus, in the era of cold weapons,

249
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,720
humans had limited fighting power.

250
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:28,159
Any wild beast

251
00:13:28,159 --> 00:13:29,279
posed a serious threat

252
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,519
to their lives.

253
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:32,679
So drawing a giant snake isn't a surprise.

254
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:35,879
Then, at such blessing ceremonies,

255
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:36,759
this, this...

256
00:13:36,759 --> 00:13:38,519
the leader of this region

257
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,639
is holding a pearl.

258
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:41,159
Could it be the Lingxiao Pearl?

259
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,600
Uncle Min, Uncle Min, Uncle Min.

260
00:13:43,159 --> 00:13:44,919
These are pictographs.

261
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,600
It takes time to decipher.

262
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,240
Give He Shutong some time.

263
00:13:48,279 --> 00:13:50,120
You have to let her think it through.

264
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,440
Fine, fine, you think then.

265
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:54,000
You've been thinking all morning.

266
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,000
It mentions here

267
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:57,440
that all Mengna Valley rulers were female.

268
00:14:00,519 --> 00:14:02,080
What follows is likely

269
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,399
the ruling class of Mengna Valley

270
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:05,200
fabricating feudal superstitions

271
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,519
to intimidate and rule the commoners.

272
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:09,360
What kind of stories could

273
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,200
Mengna Valley's rulers make up?

274
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,600
The book says

275
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,480
after each queen of Mengna Valley dies,

276
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:17,240
a new queen will be born among the people,

277
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:19,039
chosen by the serpent god.

278
00:14:19,919 --> 00:14:21,879
China's ancient emperors

279
00:14:21,879 --> 00:14:22,960
followed hereditary succession.

280
00:14:23,919 --> 00:14:26,639
What's going on with this Mengna Valley?

281
00:14:26,799 --> 00:14:29,120
Who knows who the serpent god

282
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,120
will choose as the queen?

